metadata.name: canCAT #1
metadata.description:
canCATs by canVERSE.

An in-game collectible game piece of four beautifully constructed 3D cats. Limited to a supply of just 1,000.  

Each canCAT entitles the owner not only to a super hi-res PFP, but also access to play with their canCATs as game pieces within canVERSE in several table-top games.  

More games and limited edition pieces are coming soon. All canCAT Holders are also rewarded with a spot on the guaranteed list for the canVERSE NFT in 2023.
